## Runbook

### New machine setup
```
git clone https://github.com/anrakprojects/google-ads-automation
cd google-ads-automation
python setup.py
```
Setup takes ~5 minutes. Follow prompts. Opens browser for Google auth.

### Daily monitoring
```
python scripts/daily_monitor.py
```
Read output. If RED flag: run `/ads-council`.

### Monthly market intel
```
python scripts/monthly_scraper.py
```
Then run `/ads-council` to analyze.

### Creating a new campaign
```
python scripts/campaign_interview.py
```
Resume anytime if interrupted. Then run `/ads-council` for GO/NO-GO.

### LLM Council
Invoke in Claude Code: `/ads-council`
Council reads CAMPAIGN_BRIEF.md + latest review files.
Produces GO / NO-GO verdict. You confirm before anything is acted on.

